'''[[nitrogen]] [[cycle]]'''
# the [[natural]] [[circulation]] of nitrogen, in which [[atmospheric]] nitrogen is converted to nitrogen [[oxide]]s by [[lightning]] and [[deposited]] in the [[soil]] by [[rain]] where it is [[assimilated]] by [[plant]]s and either eaten by [[animal]]s (and returned as [[faeces]]) or [[decompose]]d back to [[elemental]] nitrogen by [[bacteria]].